    <h1>MORAL</h1>
    <lg>
        <l>From Franklin Hyde’s adventure, <action>learn</action></l>
        <l>To <action>pass</action> your Leisure Time</l>
        <l>In Cleanly Merriment, and turn</l>
        <l>From <earth>Mud</earth> and Ooze and Slime</l>
        <l>And every form of Nastiness—</l>
        <l>But, on the other Hand,</l>
        <l>Children in ordinary Dress</l>
        <l>May always <action>play</action> with <earth>Sand.</earth></l>
